      "text": "Patient Static:\nAge: 65\nSex: male\nTrauma type: blunt trauma\n\nRecent Vitals:\nHour T-2: Temp 37.1, HR 92\nHour T-1: Temp 37.8, HR 105\nHour T-0: Temp 38.4, HR 118\n\nLatest Labs:\nCreatinine: 1.4, measured 3 hours ago\nLactate: 2.1, measured 2 hours ago\n\nDaily Summary:\nD-1: stable ventilation, increasing heart rate,\nmild fever\n\nCXR:\nLatest CXR at T-3. Image embedding\navailable. Report summary: low lung volume, no\npneumothorax.\n\nTask:\nPredict next-hour ICU events.",
